# With a priviledged or user account we have to set the user rights for the Shared folder as below: 
  chown root:root /Shared 

# We then proceed to setup the rights for the individual folder as below: 
  chown root:external /Shared/user2

#Within user2 incoming directory we can set the file with below rights allowing users belonging to internal group access the file ane write, read or execute within the folder. 
  chown user2:Internal /Shared/user2/Incoming 
